author: henrib
msg: * Control over whether unknown variables, methods and constructors made independent from JexlArithmetic leniency flag; JexlEngine thus regains a strict flag that controls this aspect of the behavior.
* Added ReadonlyContext that, as its name stand, will not allow  variables to be set or created.

msg: Make sure ENABLE CONDSTORE and ENABLE QRESYNC does get treated as CONDSTORE enabling command as stated in the QRESYNC RFC. See IMAP-307
